divs: Sighting DetailsFilmed a (ufo?) during the Avalon Airshow didn't see it until I viewed some footage later that day, a silver disk shaped object passed over the top of a jet, the object passed at a very high speed and was only visable in 2 frames but at the end of the video you also see another dark object passing by at a very fast speed.. I also took some still shots off the plasma..
Summary: Did some filming at the Avalon Airshow just outside Melbourne and seen later something odd in the video
